    "On the other hand, a comparison of BFLDL with benchmarks found that the BFLDL exceeded cutting-edge works in terms of accuracy and AUC.Also, future studies would involve real-time deepfake detection accomplished using online intrusions that claim to examine both video and audio-visual data in 1-s intervals.",
